  "id": "html-1771879219898",
  "title": "Distribución de asignaturas y créditos",
  "type": "html",
  "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Justificación - Oferta Internacional - Unitrópico</title>\n  <!-- Fuente Montserrat y CSS base -->\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../css_presentaciones/unitropico_base.css\">\n  <style>\n    /* =========================\n       ESTILOS ADICIONALES\n    ========================= */\n    html,\n    body {\n      height: 100%;\n      margin: 0;\n      overflow-x: hidden;\n      background: url(\"../img/background-1.jpg\") no-repeat center center fixed;\n      background-size: cover;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    /* Navbar */\n    .navbar-img {\n      width: 100%;\n      background: var(--verde-1);\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    .navbar-img img {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: auto;\n      max-height: 110px;\n      object-fit: contain;\n      display: block;\n    }\n\n    /* Contenedor principal */\n    .container {\n      max-width: 1100px;\n      margin: 30px auto;\n      padding: 0 25px;\n    }\n\n    /* Estilos de la tabla de Componentes Formativos */\n    .comp-table-container {\n      width: 100%;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      margin-bottom: 50px;\n    }\n\n    .comp-table {\n      width: 100%;\n      border-collapse: collapse;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n    }\n\n    .comp-table th,\n    .comp-table td {\n      border: 1px solid #004b40;\n      padding: 12px 15px;\n    }\n\n    .comp-table th {\n      background-color: #004b40;\n      color: #ffffff;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 1.05rem;\n    }\n\n    /* Estilos de fuente dentro de la tabla */\n    .td-bold-green {\n      color: #004b40;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .td-normal-green {\n      color: #004b40;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .td-bold-white {\n      color: #ffffff;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .td-normal-white {\n      color: #ffffff;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    /* Filas por temática */\n    .row-white {\n      background-color: #ffffff;\n    }\n\n    .row-khaki {\n      background-color: #b0a171;\n      /* Color verde oliva/caqui del diseño */\n    }\n\n    /* Alineación de Total Inferior */\n    .total-left {\n      text-align: left;\n      padding-left: 20px !important;\n    }\n\n    /* Responsive */\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n      .container {\n        margin: 15px;\n        padding: 0 15px;\n      }\n\n      .comp-table th,\n      .comp-table td {\n        padding: 8px 10px;\n        font-size: 0.85rem;\n      }\n\n      .section-header-line h2 {\n        font-size: 1.5rem !important;\n      }\n\n      .line-gold {\n        width: 100% !important;\n        max-width: 550px;\n      }\n\n      .line-gray {\n        width: 80% !important;\n        max-width: 450px;\n      }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <!-- Navbar de imagen -->\n  <div class=\"navbar-img\">\n    <img src=\"media/denominacion/navbar.png\" alt=\"Navbar Unitropico\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n    <!-- Título del artículo (alineado izquierda) -->\n    <div class=\"top-left-title subtitulo text-verde-1\">\n      <span class=\"text-bronce-1\">Artículo 2.5.3.2.3.2.4.</span> Aspectos curriculares - a) Componentes formativos\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Encabezado centrado -->\n    <div class=\"section-header-line\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 2.1rem; line-height: 1.3; color: #004b40; margin: 0 0 10px 0;\">\n        Distribución de asignaturas y créditos por<br>\n        componente y agrupación del <strong style=\"font-weight: 800;\">programa de<br>Ingeniería en Inteligencia\n          Artificial</strong>\n      </h2>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0px;\">\n        <div class=\"line-gold\" style=\"width: 550px; height: 3px; background-color: #ba9b5e; border-radius: 2px;\"></div>\n        <div class=\"line-gray\" style=\"width: 450px; height: 6px; background-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 3px;\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Contenido: Tabla de Componentes -->\n    <div class=\"comp-table-container\">\n      <table class=\"comp-table\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th style=\"width: 20%;\">Componente</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 26%;\">Agrupación</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 13.5%;\">Asignaturas</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 13.5%;\">Créditos</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 13.5%;\">Porcentaje</th>\n            <th style=\"width: 13.5%;\">Total</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <!-- Bloque: Formación Profesional -->\n          <tr class=\"row-white\">\n            <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td-bold-green\">Formación<br>Profesional</td>\n            <td class=\"td-normal-green\">Fundamentación</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">13</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">38</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">25.6%</td>\n            <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td-bold-green\">69.5%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"row-white\">\n            <td class=\"td-normal-green\">Profundización</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">24</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">65</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">43.9%</td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Bloque: Praxis Investigativa -->\n          <tr class=\"row-khaki\">\n            <td rowspan=\"3\" class=\"td-bold-white\">Praxis<br>Investigativa</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">Fundamentos de<br>Investigación</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">3</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">6</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">4.1%</td>\n            <td rowspan=\"3\" class=\"td-bold-white\">9.5%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"row-khaki\">\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">Praxis Investigativa<br>Específica</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">1</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">4</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">2.7%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"row-khaki\">\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">Trabajo de Grado</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">1</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">4</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">2.7%</td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Bloque: Formación Integral -->\n          <tr class=\"row-white\">\n            <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td-bold-green\">Formación<br>Integral</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">Competencias<br>genéricas</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">5</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">12</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">8.1%</td>\n            <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"td-bold-green\">12.2%</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr class=\"row-white\">\n            <td class=\"td-normal-green\">Identidad Institucional</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">3</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">6</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">4.1%</td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Bloque: Libre Elección -->\n          <tr class=\"row-khaki\">\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">Libre Elección</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">Agrupación única</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">4</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">13</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">8.8%</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-white\">8.8%</td>\n          </tr>\n\n          <!-- Fila de Total -->\n          <tr class=\"row-white\">\n            <td colspan=\"2\" class=\"total-left td-bold-green\">Total</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">54</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">148</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">100%</td>\n            <td class=\"td-bold-green\">100%</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</body>\n\n</html>",
  "allowScripts": true,
  "hotspots": []
}